{{> layouts/header}}
{{> layouts/gnb}}

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h2 class="mb-4 fw-bold">정산 결과</h2>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-end mb-3">
        <form action="/settlements/trip/{{tripId}}" method="get" class="d-flex align-items-center">
            <label for="totalMembers" class="me-2 fw-bold text-nowrap">정산 인원 수:</label>
            <input type="number" id="totalMembers" name="totalMembers" class="form-control me-2" style="width: 80px;" value="{{totalMembers}}" min="1" required>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary text-nowrap">적용</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
            <h4 class="mb-3">총 지출: {{totalExpense}}원</h4>
            <h4 class="text-primary fw-bold">1인당 부담 금액: {{perPerson}}원</h4>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-header bg-light">
            <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">결제자별 정산 내역</h5>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            {{#settlements}}
                <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center p-3">
                    <span class="fw-bold">{{key}}</span>
                    <span>{{value}}원</span>
                </li>
            {{/settlements}}
        </ul>
        <div class="card-footer text-muted text-center" style="font-size: 0.9em;">
            양수(+)는 받아야 할 금액, 음수(-)는 내야 할 금액을 의미합니다.<br>
            결제 내역이 없는 멤버는 1인당 부담 금액만큼 내야 합니다.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/expenses/trip/{{tripId}}" class="btn btn-secondary px-4">지출 목록으로</a>
    </div>
</div>

{{> layouts/footer}}